N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5601.4 - Processing

State Regulations

The commission shall process only complete applications. The processing of any application shall not constitute any agreement or
acceptance by the commission that the requirements of Article 14 of the Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding Law and this Chapter have been
satisfied. Notes
